  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the sous-vide machine to 130 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "In a blender, combine soy sauce, rice vinegar, garlic, ginger, and clear honey, and blend until smooth",
    "Place the pork shoulder in a sous-vide bag and pour the blended marinade over it",
    "Seal the bag and cook for 24 hours",
    "Remove the pork from the bag and slice it into thin strips",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together sesame oil and a pinch of salt",
    "Brush the sesame oil mixture over the sliced pork",
    "Assemble the ssam by placing a few slices of pork onto a lettuce leaf and garnishing with green onions",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy"
  ],
